{"about_the_game":"<strong>Joseon-Fantasy Detective Visual Novel</strong><br><br>---<br><strong>1. Episode Composition</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Titlecard_E102_620.png?t=1724590325\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Titlecard_E103_620.png?t=1724590325\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Titlecard_E104_620.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Titlecard_E105_620.png?t=1724590325\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Titlecard_E106_620.png?t=1724590325\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Titlecard_E107_620.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><br>- A monster-related murder case unfolds in the eight provinces of Joseon. Play 6 detective episodes based on local korean folklore and uncover the truth behind the cases.<br>- Each episode has 3 to 4 multiple endings.<br><br>---<br><strong>2. Investigation</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/BG_1.png?t=1724590325\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/BG_2.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><br>- Investigate the scene of the incident and collect clues necessary to solve the case.<br>- Talk to NPC characters to obtain testimonies.<br>- Use the clues and testimonies to make deductions.<br>- Combine the deductions to reach a conclusion of the case. There is only one truth among many conclusions.<br><br>---<br><strong>3. Confrontation</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Monster_2.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><br>- If you correctly identify the culprit or the monster behind the incident, you will engage in a one-on-one logical battle.<br>- Expose the villain's lies and land a strike by presenting clues.<br><br>---<br><strong>4. Character Chemistry</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/Dialogue_0.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><br>- The player embarks on a journey with colleague Jo Gun-Gwan from the perspective of Jeong Do-sa.<br>- Experience the story of Jeong Do-sa and Jo Gun-Gwan growing together as they encounter various cases.<br>- If you need hints during gameplay, you can always consult Jo Gun-Gwan.<br><br>---<br><strong>5. NPCs</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/NPC_0.png?t=1724590325\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/NPC_1.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/NPC_2.png?t=1724590325\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/NPC_3.png?t=1724590325\" /><br><br>- Talk with over 30 characters in 6 episodes.<br>- Monsters, Monks, and Villagers all have their say in the weird case that is going on.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724590325","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/page.bg.jpg?t=1724590325","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724590325","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/capsule_18